<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #d97706;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .meeting-details {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d97706;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Senate Meeting Reminder</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Dear {{memberName}},</p>
            
            <p>This is a reminder of an upcoming Senate meeting:</p>
            
            <div class="meeting-details">
                <p><strong>Meeting Title:</strong> {{meetingTitle}}</p>
                <p><strong>Scheduled Date & Time:</strong> {{scheduledAt}}</p>
                <p><strong>Venue:</strong> {{venue}}</p>
                <p><strong>Prayer Submission Deadline:</strong> {{prayerDeadline}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please ensure your attendance and submit any opening or closing prayers to the Senate Secretariat by the deadline.</p>
            
            <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">Access Portal</a>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the Senate Secretariat.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            COELS Senate Office</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 COELS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
